B. Brent, p-adic continuity for exponents in product decomposition of the j-invariant, Answer 3 by W. Zudilin
program: (PARI) {a(n) = local(A, S); if( n<1, 0, A = 1 + x * O(x^n); S = x * ellj( x * A ); for( k = 1, n-1, S *= (A - x^k) ^ polcoeff( S, k)); - polcoeff( S, n))}
